until the master's return.

281
00:20:35,819 --> 00:20:39,756
And who do I have
to thank for ruining my rug?

282
00:20:39,823 --> 00:20:41,225
Hanzo Hasashi.

283
00:20:41,292 --> 00:20:45,062
Your reputation precedes you,
Hanzo Hasashi.

284
00:20:45,129 --> 00:20:46,897
Welcome. Though,

285
00:20:46,964 --> 00:20:50,034
I'm not entirely sure
how you made it here.

286
00:20:50,101 --> 00:20:53,237
What is it you want, Hanzo?

287
00:20:53,304 --> 00:20:54,872
To return home.

288
00:20:54,939 --> 00:20:57,141
To seek my revenge.

289
00:20:57,208 --> 00:20:58,476
Home?

290
00:20:58,542 --> 00:21:00,411
[laughs]

291
00:21:00,478 --> 00:21:02,612
You can't return home.

292
00:21:03,581 --> 00:21:04,482
[grunts]

293
00:21:04,548 --> 00:21:06,550
You will do as I say,

294
00:21:06,616 --> 00:21:09,186
or I will flay you alive.

295
00:21:11,155 --> 00:21:12,356
[Hanzo grunts]

296
00:21:15,960 --> 00:21:18,795
Did you think me
defenseless, dog?

297
00:21:18,863 --> 00:21:21,398
In my realm no less.

298
00:21:21,465 --> 00:21:22,699
[Hanzo groaning]

299
00:21:22,765 --> 00:21:24,969
You may be a vengeful spirit,

300
00:21:25,035 --> 00:21:28,139
but even they
have their limits.

301
00:21:28,205 --> 00:21:29,907
[Hanzo screaming]

302
00:21:32,243 --> 00:21:34,078
[groaning]

303
00:21:42,286 --> 00:21:46,689
Besides, that's not what
you really want, is it?

304
00:21:48,725 --> 00:21:51,395
Once a generation,
there is a tournament.

305
00:21:52,496 --> 00:21:53,796
During that time,

306
00:21:53,864 --> 00:21:55,599
the veil is lifted,

307
00:21:55,665 --> 00:21:59,769
so that warriors may gather to
fight on behalf of their realm.

308
00:21:59,836 --> 00:22:01,704
I can send you there.

309
00:22:01,771 --> 00:22:05,708
[pants] Why would
I fight for you?

310
00:22:05,775 --> 00:22:09,313
[Quan Chi] Because he will
be in attendance.

311
00:22:09,380 --> 00:22:11,148
[panting]

312
00:22:13,683 --> 00:22:15,886
What do you want?

313
00:22:15,953 --> 00:22:20,858
[Quan Chi] Good, skilled
and smart. [laughs]

314
00:22:22,792 --> 00:22:24,161
Long ago,

315
00:22:24,228 --> 00:22:28,165
my master, Shinnok,
was unjustly imprisoned.

316
00:22:28,232 --> 00:22:31,202
This is the key to his release.

317
00:22:31,268 --> 00:22:34,238
It's being kept
at the temple of Shang Tsung,

318
00:22:34,305 --> 00:22:35,805
the putrid mortal

319
00:22:35,873 --> 00:22:38,909
that has the favor
of the emperor of Outworld.

320
00:22:38,976 --> 00:22:42,279
The tournament will take place
on his island.

321
00:22:42,346 --> 00:22:44,781
Get me that key.

322
00:22:44,847 --> 00:22:47,451
Once my master is released,

323
00:22:47,518 --> 00:22:49,653
he can return your family.

324
00:22:49,719 --> 00:22:53,624
Even you,
back to the mortal realm.

325
00:22:53,691 --> 00:22:56,894
Do we understand
each other, Hanzo?

326
00:22:59,296 --> 00:23:01,432
Hanzo is dead.

327
00:23:01,498 --> 00:23:03,434
Call me Scorpion.

328
00:23:07,238 --> 00:23:09,839
[boat horn blows]

329
00:23:11,609 --> 00:23:14,378
Hold the boat! I'm coming!

330
00:23:14,445 --> 00:23:15,879
[panting]

331
00:23:15,946 --> 00:23:18,015
[grunting]

332
00:23:19,749 --> 00:23:22,453
Coming through. I'm co...

333
00:23:22,519 --> 00:23:25,623
Whoa, whoa... [grunts]

334
00:23:25,689 --> 00:23:26,857
[Sonya] Hmm.

335
00:23:31,095 --> 00:23:31,962
Mmm?

336
00:23:35,899 --> 00:23:39,903
[clears throat] Hope no fans saw that.
I'm wearing slip-ons.

337
00:23:44,508 --> 00:23:47,044
Lui Kang,
of the White Lotus Society.

338
00:23:47,111 --> 00:23:49,713
Johnny Cage,
of the superstar variety,

339
00:23:49,779 --> 00:23:51,682
but you probably knew that.

340
00:23:51,749 --> 00:23:53,250
And you are?

341
00:23:53,917 --> 00:23:55,586
Not interested.

342
00:23:55,653 --> 00:23:58,155
Oh, you will be.
They always are.

343
00:23:58,222 --> 00:24:00,391
So, you guys
in this thing, too?

344
00:24:00,457 --> 00:24:03,594
Yes, I have trained
many years for this moment.

345
00:24:03,661 --> 00:24:05,129
Oh, yeah? Listen,

346
00:24:05,195 --> 00:24:06,530
I love acting classes and all,

347
00:24:06,597 --> 00:24:09,033
but they're really
kind of a time suck.

348
00:24:09,099 --> 00:24:10,800
You know what I mean?
No? Anyway,

349
00:24:10,868 --> 00:24:13,137
my agent said this would
really put me back on the map.

350
00:24:13,203 --> 00:24:15,539
Kind of a back-end-deal-type-of-thing.
Should be fun.

351
00:24:15,606 --> 00:24:17,840
[Raiden] We are
approaching the veil.

352
00:24:19,677 --> 00:24:20,810
Who is that? Let me guess.

353
00:24:20,878 --> 00:24:22,913
He's kind of like
our, uh, Merlin.

354
00:24:22,980 --> 00:24:24,682
That is Lord Raiden.

355
00:24:24,748 --> 00:24:26,283
Protector of Earthrealm.

356
00:24:26,350 --> 00:24:28,986
Boom! Nailed it.
Wait, Earthrealm?

357
00:24:29,053 --> 00:24:30,721
Did you guys get
a script already or something?

358
00:24:30,788 --> 00:24:32,089
Look, I'd love a copy.

359
00:24:32,156 --> 00:24:34,224
I have no idea
what you're talking about,

360
00:24:34,291 --> 00:24:36,560
but I am pretty good
at improv. So, uh...

361
00:24:37,928 --> 00:24:39,863
Lord Raiden, right?

362
00:24:39,930 --> 00:24:40,998
Good to meet you.

363
00:24:41,065 --> 00:24:44,435
So, tell me more
about this veil.

364
00:24:44,501 --> 00:24:46,236
The space between realms,

365
00:24:46,303 --> 00:24:49,807
to prevent Outworld
from merging with Earthrealm.

366
00:24:49,873 --> 00:24:51,041
Prevented by what?

367
00:24:51,108 --> 00:24:52,910
Always the soldier,

368
00:24:52,976 --> 00:24:55,012
evaluating risks.

369
00:24:55,079 --> 00:24:59,750
What guards the veil is of less
consequence than why it does so.

370
00:24:59,817 --> 00:25:02,052
If Shao Kahn
wins this tournament,

371
00:25:02,119 --> 00:25:05,622
Earth, as you know it,
will cease to exist.

372
00:25:05,689 --> 00:25:07,024
Not to fear, Lord Raiden.

373
00:25:07,091 --> 00:25:08,625
I, Johnny Cage,

374
00:25:08,692 --> 00:25:11,161
will make sure that
Earthrealm, [softly] so dumb,

375
00:25:11,228 --> 00:25:13,130
will be safe from harm.

376
00:25:13,197 --> 00:25:15,032
You have my word on it.

377
00:25:21,372 --> 00:25:24,141
Lord Raiden,
these are the champions you gathered?

378
00:25:24,208 --> 00:25:26,410
You doubt my choices?

379
00:25:26,477 --> 00:25:27,945
No, I just meant...

380
00:25:28,011 --> 00:25:31,281
You see only what is in front
of you, Lui Kang,

381
00:25:31,348 --> 00:25:33,250
but your eyes deceive you.

382
00:25:33,317 --> 00:25:36,320
It is what is inside
that matters.

383
00:25:36,387 --> 00:25:37,856
Sonya Blade,

384
00:25:37,921 --> 00:25:40,124
a most formidable warrior.

385
00:25:40,190 --> 00:25:42,493
She has had
to prove herself against many

386
00:25:42,559 --> 00:25:46,897
who thought she was
nothing more than a weak girl.

387
00:25:46,964 --> 00:25:49,666
Believe me,
she is anything but.

388
00:25:49,733 --> 00:25:53,470
And him? He only seems to be concerned
about himself and material wealth.

389
00:25:53,537 --> 00:25:56,073
[muttering angrily]

390
00:25:56,140 --> 00:25:57,574
[Raiden] That will
keep him alive,

391
00:25:57,641 --> 00:26:01,044
until he finds something more
to care about.

392
00:26:01,111 --> 00:26:03,914
Something greater
than himself to live for.

393
00:26:03,981 --> 00:26:05,749
[Johnny Cage]
Are you kidding me?

394
00:26:05,816 --> 00:26:08,152
I paid extra for international,
and I can't even get a signal.

395
00:26:08,218 --> 00:26:10,220
Uh, Raiden, are getting one?

396
00:26:10,287 --> 00:26:11,355
[grunts]

397
00:26:17,094 --> 00:26:18,429
What in the...

398
00:26:21,532 --> 00:26:22,699
[shrieks]

399
00:26:22,766 --> 00:26:24,001
Stay in the vessel.

400
00:26:24,067 --> 00:26:26,170
It is under
Lord Raiden's protection.

401
00:26:26,236 --> 00:26:28,839
Out there,
there's nothing good.

402
00:26:28,907 --> 00:26:30,941
Oh, right.

403
00:26:31,008 --> 00:26:32,309
Paparazzi.

404
00:26:33,444 --> 00:26:34,611
We've arrived.

405
00:27:12,583 --> 00:27:13,984
Look.

406
00:27:24,027 --> 00:27:26,029
That must be the bad guy.

407
00:27:29,633 --> 00:27:31,668
One at a time, everybody.
One at a time.

408
00:27:31,735 --> 00:27:34,104
Brought enough
for everyone. Okay.

409
00:27:34,171 --> 00:27:35,506
Where'd you guys
put my trailer?

410
00:27:35,572 --> 00:27:37,808
I'd like to freshen up
before we start shooting.

411
00:27:37,876 --> 00:27:39,343
Ugh.

412
00:27:42,546 --> 00:27:44,715
He has no idea
what he is doing.

413
00:27:44,781 --> 00:27:46,116
Should we tell him?

414
00:27:46,183 --> 00:27:48,920
His journey
is one of discovery.

415
00:27:48,987 --> 00:27:51,655
Besides, I find it amusing.

416
00:28:04,401 --> 00:28:07,271
Remember our deal, Scorpion.

417
00:28:10,975 --> 00:28:13,143
[Johnny Cage panting]

418
00:28:15,980 --> 00:28:17,381
[sighs]

419
00:28:37,134 --> 00:28:38,302
Whoa.

420
00:28:41,271 --> 00:28:42,839
[crowd cheering]

421
00:28:49,146 --> 00:28:50,514
[burps]

422
00:28:51,081 --> 00:28:52,516
Yeah! Yeah!

423
00:28:59,857 --> 00:29:00,992
[grunts]

424
00:29:01,059 --> 00:29:02,726
[grunts]

425
00:29:02,793 --> 00:29:04,161
[crowd cheering]

426
00:29:18,642 --> 00:29:20,110
Be on guard.

427
00:29:20,177 --> 00:29:22,512
Shang Tsung
is not to be trusted.

428
00:29:22,579 --> 00:29:24,648
Oh, look!
Craft services. Great!

429
00:29:24,715 --> 00:29:26,416
[Sonya sighs]

430
00:29:39,229 --> 00:29:42,633
[sniffs] Hey, do you know if
any of this stuff is organic?

431
00:29:42,699 --> 00:29:43,935
[snarls]

432
00:29:44,002 --> 00:29:45,769
Just asking. Geez!

433
00:29:53,143 --> 00:29:55,245
Now is your chance.

434
00:30:00,852 --> 00:30:02,619
[drums beating]

435
00:30:09,760 --> 00:30:11,863
[all cheering]

436
00:30:22,773 --> 00:30:24,541
[Shang Tsung] <i>In the beginning,</i>

437
00:30:24,608 --> 00:30:26,743
<i>were the elder Gods.</i>

438
00:30:27,811 --> 00:30:29,579
<i>In their wisdom,</i>

439
00:30:29,646 --> 00:30:31,448
<i>they created a tournament</i>

440
00:30:31,515 --> 00:30:36,219
<i>to safeguard each realm
from the threat of invasion.</i>

441
00:30:36,286 --> 00:30:37,989
<i>Once a generation,</i>

442
00:30:38,056 --> 00:30:40,457
<i>the finest warriors
must do battle</i>

443
00:30:40,524 --> 00:30:43,427
<i>to decide the fate
of their realm.</i>

444
00:30:43,493 --> 00:30:46,030
<i>The winner will be
granted long life</i>

445
00:30:46,097 --> 00:30:47,831
<i>and great power.</i>

446
00:30:47,899 --> 00:30:51,468
<i>If one realm wins
the tournament ten times,</i>

447
00:30:51,535 --> 00:30:54,138
<i>they will have the right
to merge with the other,</i>

448
00:30:54,237 --> 00:30:56,908
<i>and rule as they see fit.</i>

449
00:30:56,974 --> 00:30:59,276
<i>I, Shang Tsung,</i>

450
00:30:59,342 --> 00:31:01,845
<i>emissary of
the great Shao Kahn,</i>

451
00:31:01,913 --> 00:31:04,082
<i>emperor of Outworld,</i>

452
00:31:04,148 --> 00:31:08,719
<i>winner of the last nine
tournaments against Earthrealm,</i>

453
00:31:08,785 --> 00:31:12,322
welcome you
to Mortal Kombat.

454
00:31:12,389 --> 00:31:15,659
- [crowd cheering]
- [man] Mortal Kombat!

455
00:31:37,247 --> 00:31:38,883
[grunting]

456
00:32:02,672 --> 00:32:03,673
Now,

457
00:32:03,740 --> 00:32:05,910
as host of this tournament,

458
00:32:05,977 --> 00:32:10,148
I think it only fitting that
I provide you with some...

459
00:32:10,214 --> 00:32:12,415
entertainment. [claps]

460
00:32:20,690 --> 00:32:21,758
Kano.

461
00:32:25,263 --> 00:32:26,663
[grunts]

462
00:32:29,200 --> 00:32:30,968
Jax! [grunts]

463
00:32:33,336 --> 00:32:35,405
[cheering]

464
00:32:41,245 --> 00:32:42,646
Jax! [grunts]

465
00:32:44,148 --> 00:32:45,950
Listen, you son of a bitch,

466
00:32:46,017 --> 00:32:48,718
you better open this,
whatever it is,

467
00:32:48,785 --> 00:32:52,489
or I'm gonna use your ass as
my own personal punching bag.

468
00:32:52,556 --> 00:32:54,091
Oh, that is so hot.

469
00:32:54,158 --> 00:32:56,593
[Sonya grunting]

470
00:32:58,229 --> 00:33:00,397
- [Jax] Princess.
- Asshole.

471
00:33:00,463 --> 00:33:02,133
I told you to wait for me.

472
00:33:02,200 --> 00:33:03,500
I got excited.

473
00:33:03,567 --> 00:33:06,270
You got caught
by that idiot Kano.

474
00:33:06,336 --> 00:33:09,273
[sighs] Yeah, that too.

475
00:33:09,339 --> 00:33:13,743
Unless you want me to rip that
pencil-thin mustache off your face,

476
00:33:13,810 --> 00:33:17,081
I think it's best
you let me go, old man.

477
00:33:17,148 --> 00:33:18,682
Absolutely.

478
00:33:18,748 --> 00:33:21,319
You are free
to leave at any time.

479
00:33:21,384 --> 00:33:23,720
The doorway is right there.

480
00:33:25,522 --> 00:33:26,790
Of course,

481
00:33:26,858 --> 00:33:29,227
you have to get past
my champion.

482
00:33:29,293 --> 00:33:31,595
[drums beating]

483
00:33:31,661 --> 00:33:35,765
[chanting] Goro! Goro! Goro!

484
00:33:36,901 --> 00:33:39,904
[all chanting]
Goro! Goro! Goro!

485
00:33:44,507 --> 00:33:46,944
[chanting continues]

486
00:33:52,415 --> 00:33:54,852
[chanting continues]

487
00:34:02,927 --> 00:34:04,128
What the hell?

488
00:34:05,462 --> 00:34:07,430
[crowd cheering]

489
00:34:10,902 --> 00:34:11,936
[gasps]

490
00:34:18,642 --> 00:34:20,177
[Goro growls]

491
00:34:22,280 --> 00:34:24,048
Jax! No!

492
00:34:24,115 --> 00:34:26,483
Relax, kid. I've got this.

493
00:34:26,549 --> 00:34:28,252
All right, ugly.

494
00:34:28,319 --> 00:34:29,854
You wanna dance?

495
00:34:29,921 --> 00:34:31,255
Let's dance.

496
00:34:31,322 --> 00:34:33,590
[grunts]

497
00:34:34,091 --> 00:34:35,192
[gasps]

498
00:34:35,259 --> 00:34:36,559
[grunting]

499
00:34:39,629 --> 00:34:40,830
[chuckles]

500
00:34:43,134 --> 00:34:44,434
[grunts]

501
00:34:56,446 --> 00:34:57,781
[Raiden] I wouldn't.

502
00:35:01,185 --> 00:35:02,719
Let me guess.

503
00:35:02,786 --> 00:35:06,489
Quan Chi promised you life
if you would do his bidding.

504
00:35:06,924 --> 00:35:09,226
Ah... No.

505
00:35:09,293 --> 00:35:12,063
Not you. Someone else.

506
00:35:12,129 --> 00:35:13,830
Someone you lost.

507
00:35:13,898 --> 00:35:15,866
Someone you care about.

508
00:35:15,933 --> 00:35:19,070
Do you think Quan Chi
is a man to be trusted?

509
00:35:19,136 --> 00:35:21,372
[Scorpion]
What choice do I have?

510
00:35:21,439 --> 00:35:23,274
We all have choices.

511
00:35:23,341 --> 00:35:24,774
Live in the past,

512
00:35:24,841 --> 00:35:27,711
or live for the future.

513
00:35:27,777 --> 00:35:30,613
The key won't
solve your problems.

514
00:35:30,680 --> 00:35:34,218
It will, however,
create new ones.

515
00:35:34,285 --> 00:35:35,618
[Scorpion] And my revenge?

516
00:35:35,685 --> 00:35:39,190
Revenge is too heavy
a burden to carry.

517
00:35:39,256 --> 00:35:40,824
You are a free man.

518
00:35:40,891 --> 00:35:42,994
It's time you start
acting like it.

519
00:35:53,004 --> 00:35:55,172
[Jax groans]

520
00:35:55,239 --> 00:35:57,074
[Jax panting]

521
00:35:58,708 --> 00:36:00,344
- [crowd cheering]
- [man laughing]

522
00:36:00,411 --> 00:36:02,712
[indistinct shouting]

523
00:36:02,779 --> 00:36:04,647
[Jax groaning]

524
00:36:14,557 --> 00:36:16,626
[groans]

525
00:36:22,299 --> 00:36:23,633
[grunts]

526
00:36:25,369 --> 00:36:29,006
Really, Goro, you shouldn't
play with your food.

527
00:36:29,073 --> 00:36:30,908
[Goro growls]

528
00:36:36,579 --> 00:36:38,848
[groaning, screaming]

529
00:36:40,650 --> 00:36:42,019
[bones snapping]

530
00:36:42,953 --> 00:36:44,788
[laughs]

531
00:36:44,855 --> 00:36:47,158
[Jax screaming]

532
00:36:47,224 --> 00:36:49,026
Stop it! You'll kill him.

533
00:36:49,093 --> 00:36:51,095
That's the idea.

534
00:36:51,162 --> 00:36:52,496
Finish him.

535
00:36:52,562 --> 00:36:54,498
[Jax screaming]

536
00:36:54,564 --> 00:36:56,566
[bones snapping]

537
00:36:58,169 --> 00:36:59,636
[screams]

538
00:36:59,702 --> 00:37:01,038
[all cheering]

539
00:37:01,105 --> 00:37:02,006
No!

540
00:37:02,073 --> 00:37:03,274
[all cheering]

541
00:37:04,041 --> 00:37:05,209
Yeah!

542
00:37:12,083 --> 00:37:14,485
Pfft! Fake.

543
00:37:14,552 --> 00:37:16,153
These special effects suck.

544
00:37:17,855 --> 00:37:19,924
[Goro growls]

545
00:37:20,558 --> 00:37:21,758
[Raiden] Enough!

546
00:37:21,825 --> 00:37:23,693
- [electricity crackling]
- [Goro grunts]

547
00:37:32,269 --> 00:37:35,072
