[Jax groans]

1072
01:07:44,414 --> 01:07:45,582
Wait a minute.

1073
01:07:45,649 --> 01:07:47,584
[Kano groaning]

1074
01:07:47,651 --> 01:07:49,519
- [Jax grunts]
- [bone crunching]

1075
01:07:50,988 --> 01:07:52,156
Now we can go.

1076
01:07:54,859 --> 01:07:56,394
Aah!

1077
01:07:56,459 --> 01:07:58,162
[muffled grunting]

1078
01:08:01,132 --> 01:08:03,167
[both grunting]

1079
01:08:04,601 --> 01:08:05,903
- [Goro growling]
- [Lui Kang groaning]

1080
01:08:05,970 --> 01:08:07,604
[crunching]

1081
01:08:08,705 --> 01:08:10,041
[both grunting]

1082
01:08:10,107 --> 01:08:12,542
Yes. Yes.

1083
01:08:12,609 --> 01:08:14,979
You see, Quan Chi,
the key to winning

1084
01:08:15,046 --> 01:08:18,715
is always being a few steps
ahead of your enemies.

1085
01:08:20,450 --> 01:08:21,785
[sizzling]

1086
01:08:24,188 --> 01:08:25,356
Did you think I didn't know

1087
01:08:25,423 --> 01:08:27,624
you'd betray your Emperor,
Quan Chi?

1088
01:08:27,691 --> 01:08:30,127
You're mistaken.
I would never...

1089
01:08:33,030 --> 01:08:34,597
[groans]

1090
01:08:34,664 --> 01:08:36,901
- [groaning]
- [Shang Tsung] All for what?

1091
01:08:36,968 --> 01:08:38,936
This?

1092
01:08:39,003 --> 01:08:42,206
He's been imprisoned
for a reason, Quan Chi.

1093
01:08:42,273 --> 01:08:45,675
Your sad devotion
to the mad God Shinnok,

1094
01:08:45,742 --> 01:08:48,079
- makes you as pathetic as he is.
- [groaning]

1095
01:08:48,145 --> 01:08:51,748
Soon, Earthrealm will be
Shao Kahn's,

1096
01:08:51,815 --> 01:08:54,684
and his destiny
will be complete.

1097
01:08:54,751 --> 01:08:58,055
It's too bad you won't live
long enough to see it.

1098
01:08:58,122 --> 01:08:59,156
[groaning]

1099
01:08:59,223 --> 01:09:01,225
Finish him.

1100
01:09:01,292 --> 01:09:02,759
[Lui Kang groaning]

1101
01:09:04,728 --> 01:09:06,931
[Lui Kang straining]

1102
01:09:06,998 --> 01:09:08,832
- [Lui Kang groaning]
- [Goro laughing]

1103
01:09:10,434 --> 01:09:12,669
Does it hurt?

1104
01:09:12,736 --> 01:09:14,238
[Lui Kang screams]

1105
01:09:15,272 --> 01:09:16,806
[grunting]

1106
01:09:16,874 --> 01:09:19,076
[Lui Kang screaming]

1107
01:09:22,947 --> 01:09:26,984
Soon, your weak species
will be no more.

1108
01:09:28,352 --> 01:09:29,887
[Goro grunts]

1109
01:09:40,364 --> 01:09:41,866
[groans]

1110
01:09:47,038 --> 01:09:48,272
Who dares?

1111
01:09:52,143 --> 01:09:53,010
Scorpion.

1112
01:09:56,047 --> 01:09:57,314
Impossible.

1113
01:09:57,381 --> 01:10:01,551
It would seem I underestimated
your champion, Quan Chi.

1114
01:10:02,953 --> 01:10:05,789
You are Scorpion
of Netherrealm, yes?

1115
01:10:07,791 --> 01:10:09,692
You have killed Goro.

1116
01:10:09,759 --> 01:10:12,430
Thus you must take
your rightful place

1117
01:10:12,496 --> 01:10:14,165
as the champion of Outworld.

1118
01:10:14,231 --> 01:10:17,535
I want nothing to do
with your game.

1119
01:10:17,600 --> 01:10:19,803
I've come for him.

1120
01:10:20,504 --> 01:10:22,239
[Shang Tsung laughs]

1121
01:10:22,306 --> 01:10:23,673
Interesting.

1122
01:10:24,442 --> 01:10:26,110
Defeat Lui Kang,

1123
01:10:26,177 --> 01:10:29,712
and you can have Quan Chi
to do with as you wish.

1124
01:10:29,779 --> 01:10:31,449
Defeat Lui Kang,

1125
01:10:31,515 --> 01:10:35,785
and my emperor will give you
all that you dream of.

1126
01:10:36,786 --> 01:10:39,023
Vengeance is not the way,
Scorpion.

1127
01:10:39,090 --> 01:10:40,524
Of course it is,

1128
01:10:40,590 --> 01:10:41,892
and it's yours.

1129
01:10:42,625 --> 01:10:44,228
All you have to do

1130
01:10:45,129 --> 01:10:46,263
is kill him.

1131
01:10:51,668 --> 01:10:53,736
[Lui Kang panting]

1132
01:11:02,113 --> 01:11:03,080
[exhales]

1133
01:11:03,847 --> 01:11:05,149
[Shang Tsung] Good.

1134
01:11:05,583 --> 01:11:07,284
Good.

1135
01:11:07,351 --> 01:11:10,687
What choice did he
really have, Lord Raiden?

1136
01:11:11,889 --> 01:11:14,291
There's always
another choice.

1137
01:11:20,663 --> 01:11:22,699
Now. Fight.

1138
01:11:28,906 --> 01:11:31,909
[grunts] What are you doing?

1139
01:11:31,976 --> 01:11:34,245
[Scorpion]
Living for the future.

1140
01:11:34,311 --> 01:11:36,713
- Give me the key.
- [Shang Tsung grunts]

1141
01:11:39,183 --> 01:11:40,351
You fool.

1142
01:11:40,417 --> 01:11:42,219
Shao Kahn will hear about this

1143
01:11:42,286 --> 01:11:45,089
- and kill you.
- I'm already dead.

1144
01:11:45,156 --> 01:11:46,490
Lui Kang.

1145
01:11:46,557 --> 01:11:48,926
- I yield.
- No. [groans]

1146
01:11:50,060 --> 01:11:52,196
Then the tournament
is finished.

1147
01:11:52,263 --> 01:11:53,964
Outworld has lost.

1148
01:11:54,031 --> 01:11:56,400
Earthrealm is safe.

1149
01:11:56,467 --> 01:11:57,334
[grunts]

1150
01:11:58,335 --> 01:12:01,005
I will kill you all.

1151
01:12:01,071 --> 01:12:03,307
The tournament is over,
Shang Tsung.

1152
01:12:03,374 --> 01:12:07,810
I am no longer bound
by rules of non-interference.

1153
01:12:07,878 --> 01:12:10,314
Return to your Emperor.

1154
01:12:10,381 --> 01:12:11,848
Tell him of your failure.

1155
01:12:11,916 --> 01:12:14,885
You have made a mistake,
Lord Raiden.

1156
01:12:14,952 --> 01:12:18,622
Emperor Shao Kahn
will have his revenge.

1157
01:12:18,688 --> 01:12:19,924
I'm counting on it.

1158
01:12:21,158 --> 01:12:22,126
No.

1159
01:12:24,727 --> 01:12:26,497
Without Shang Tsung's power,

1160
01:12:26,564 --> 01:12:27,865
the island will collapse.

1161
01:12:27,932 --> 01:12:29,333
We must go.

1162
01:12:30,800 --> 01:12:32,002
What about Scorpion?

1163
01:12:32,069 --> 01:12:33,803
His path lies elsewhere.

1164
01:12:33,871 --> 01:12:35,072
- But...
- Now.

1165
01:12:37,575 --> 01:12:39,742
I knew you would survive.

1166
01:12:39,809 --> 01:12:42,513
I chose you for a reason.

1167
01:12:42,580 --> 01:12:44,114
Give me the key

1168
01:12:44,181 --> 01:12:47,918
and we can leave this place
before it is destroyed.

1169
01:12:47,985 --> 01:12:49,587
[Scorpion] Come take it.

1170
01:12:49,653 --> 01:12:51,889
Like you did my family.

1171
01:12:53,591 --> 01:12:56,193
Very well. But please,

1172
01:12:56,260 --> 01:12:59,829
put up more of a fight
than your wife did.

1173
01:13:00,464 --> 01:13:02,700
[Scorpion screams]

1174
01:13:02,765 --> 01:13:03,934
[both grunt]

1175
01:13:04,868 --> 01:13:06,403
[Scorpion grunting]

1176
01:13:09,772 --> 01:13:10,975
[Quan Chi grunting]

1177
01:13:13,711 --> 01:13:15,379
[Quan Chi grunting]

1178
01:13:16,614 --> 01:13:17,948
[Scorpion groans]

1179
01:13:20,985 --> 01:13:24,722
I'm going to finish the job
my demons couldn't.

1180
01:13:24,787 --> 01:13:26,156
Die,

1181
01:13:26,223 --> 01:13:28,791
- you wretched vermin.
- [Scorpion gasping]

1182
01:13:28,859 --> 01:13:30,327
[Scorpion groaning]

1183
01:13:31,462 --> 01:13:32,329
[Scorpion grunts]

1184
01:13:32,396 --> 01:13:33,830
[bone cracking]

1185
01:13:36,033 --> 01:13:39,169
[panting] It's time to die.

1186
01:13:40,571 --> 01:13:42,640
Indeed. [growls]

1187
01:13:42,706 --> 01:13:44,341
[both grunting]

1188
01:13:47,978 --> 01:13:50,114
[grunting, roars]

1189
01:13:55,119 --> 01:13:56,819
[distant explosion]

1190
01:13:58,722 --> 01:13:59,723
[Lui Kang grunts]

1191
01:13:59,789 --> 01:14:02,825
Lui, Lord Randy. Need a lift?

1192
01:14:07,965 --> 01:14:09,033
[grunting]

1193
01:14:12,036 --> 01:14:13,304
[Scorpion grunting]

1194
01:14:17,041 --> 01:14:18,609
[Scorpion roars]

1195
01:14:18,676 --> 01:14:19,842
[grunting]

1196
01:14:19,910 --> 01:14:21,278
[bone crunching]

1197
01:14:21,345 --> 01:14:22,880
[groaning]

1198
01:14:22,946 --> 01:14:24,915
[both grunting]

1199
01:14:36,560 --> 01:14:38,028
[Scorpion growling]

1200
01:14:38,696 --> 01:14:40,197
[roaring]

1201
01:14:41,398 --> 01:14:42,599
[Scorpion grunts]

1202
01:14:44,468 --> 01:14:45,669
[Quan Chi groaning]

1203
01:14:45,736 --> 01:14:47,271
[grunting]

1204
01:14:58,782 --> 01:15:00,284
[screaming]

1205
01:15:04,555 --> 01:15:06,090
[grunting]

1206
01:15:08,659 --> 01:15:10,594
[Quan Chi screams]

1207
01:15:10,661 --> 01:15:11,995
[Quan Chi groans]

1208
01:15:16,400 --> 01:15:17,601
[bones crunching]

1209
01:15:17,668 --> 01:15:19,236
[screaming]

1210
01:15:19,303 --> 01:15:21,472
- [Scorpion] Get over here.
- [groans]

1211
01:15:26,677 --> 01:15:29,646
My God will avenge me.

1212
01:15:30,581 --> 01:15:32,883
Damn your God.

1213
01:15:32,950 --> 01:15:34,318
[groans]

1214
01:15:43,360 --> 01:15:44,995
[screaming]

1215
01:16:12,589 --> 01:16:14,258
So, is that it?

1216
01:16:14,324 --> 01:16:16,760
- Did we win?
- For now.

1217
01:16:16,827 --> 01:16:18,996
All right! Yeah!

1218
01:16:19,930 --> 01:16:21,698
Uh... May I?

1219
01:16:25,269 --> 01:16:28,005
[Johnny Cage]
All right, yeah. Mmm.

1220
01:16:28,071 --> 01:16:29,940
Hmm, cinnamon.

1221
01:16:30,841 --> 01:16:32,176
Mmm, yeah, pat me there.

1222
01:16:32,242 --> 01:16:33,878
Doesn't mean I'm gonna
break the hug.

1223
01:16:33,944 --> 01:16:35,479
- That's enough.
- [Johnny] Okay.

1224
01:16:36,780 --> 01:16:38,081
Think she'll ever like me?

1225
01:16:38,148 --> 01:16:40,117
She didn't hit you in the nuts,
did she?

1226
01:16:40,184 --> 01:16:43,387
Yes, she did, Jax.
Yes, she did.

1227
01:16:44,755 --> 01:16:46,190
I have failed you.

1228
01:16:46,256 --> 01:16:47,658
I could not defeat Goro.

1229
01:16:48,759 --> 01:16:50,427
If it wasn't for Scorpion...

1230
01:16:50,494 --> 01:16:52,329
Failed? No.

1231
01:16:52,396 --> 01:16:56,834
Your destiny was never
to defeat Goro, Lui Kang.

1232
01:16:56,901 --> 01:16:59,269
It was to defeat Shao Kahn.

1233
01:17:00,604 --> 01:17:01,805
[Shang Tsung groaning]

1234
01:17:01,873 --> 01:17:03,440
[Shao Kahn] You have failed me.

1235
01:17:04,074 --> 01:17:05,944
I'm sorry, Master.

1236
01:17:06,009 --> 01:17:08,078
It was that old fool, Raiden.

1237
01:17:08,145 --> 01:17:10,547
- He...
- [Shao Kahn] Silence!

1238
01:17:10,614 --> 01:17:12,449
Gather our forces.

1239
01:17:12,516 --> 01:17:15,452
It's time to end this game...

1240
01:17:16,253 --> 01:17:18,555
once and for all.

1241
